### 1.6 GET Expeditions - System Admin (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expeditions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.7 GET Expedition By Id - System Admin (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expeditions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.8 GET Expeditions - Travel Manager (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expeditions
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}

###

### 1.9 POST Expedition - Travel Manager (Expect 201 or 200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/expeditions
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campId": 1,
  "name": "expedition-rbac-test",
  "objective": "RBAC validation",
  "destinationDescription": "Zone A",
  "destinationLatitude": "0.0000",
  "destinationLongitude": "0.0000",
  "plannedDepartureDate": "2026-04-10T08:00:00Z",
  "actualDepartureDate": null,
  "plannedReturnDate": "2026-04-12T08:00:00Z",
  "actualReturnDate": null,
  "extraDaysAvailable": 1,
  "extraDaysUsed": 0,
  "status": "PLANNED"
}

###

### 1.10 PUT Expedition - Travel Manager (Expect 200)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/expeditions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

###

